{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775883456601,"sessionID":"ses_285190f42ffezl6ektvwERVqVL","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae71057001kJXuprBFyadzFo","messageID":"msg_d7ae7051700186kAPFq1GL1MGt","sessionID":"ses_285190f42ffezl6ektvwERVqVL","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883472567,"sessionID":"ses_285190f42ffezl6ektvwERVqVL","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae71866001yTIw4AG7Gp4bmj","messageID":"msg_d7ae7051700186kAPFq1GL1MGt","sessionID":"ses_285190f42ffezl6ektvwERVqVL","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_9a59a07fb97f4e22a1a09bb6","state":{"status":"error","input":{"content":"# Proposal: AR-040 — Python SDK/CLI 测试\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube Python SDK (`agentcube-sdk`) 编写测试套件，验证 `CodeInterpreterClient` 和 `AgentRuntimeClient` 的核心功能、HTTP 契约、异常处理和生命周期管理。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **单元测试**\n   - `CodeInterpreterClient` 生命周期：context manager、session 创建/删除、data plane 初始化失败处理\n   - `AgentRuntimeClient` 生命周期：context manager、session bootstrap、invoke\n   - `ControlPlaneClient`：create_session、delete_session、URL/token 解析\n   - `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`：execute_command、run_code、write_file、upload_file、download_file、list_files\n   - `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`：invoke、session header\n   - 异常类：`AgentCubeError`、`CommandExecutionError`、`SessionError`、`DataPlaneError`\n\n2. **HTTP 契约测试**\n   - Control plane: `POST /v1/code-interpreter`, `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}`\n   - Data plane (Code Interpreter): `POST api/execute`, `POST api/files`, `GET api/files`\n   - Data plane (Agent Runtime): `GET` bootstrap, `POST` invoke\n   - Header 验证：`x-agentcube-session-id`、`Authorization`、`Content-Type`\n\n3. **边界场景**\n   - Router URL 缺失时 `ValueError`\n   - Command 非零退出时 `CommandExecutionError`\n   - Session bootstrap 缺失 header 时 `ValueError`\n   - 404 处理返回 `True`\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- 集成测试（需要真实 Workload Manager / Router）\n- 端到端测试 (`scripts/e2e_picod_test.py`)\n- 性能/负载测试\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Benefits\n\n- **质量保障**：覆盖核心 client 方法和 HTTP 契约，减少回归风险\n- **文档价值**：测试即文档，明确期望行为\n- **重构安全**：后续改写 internal 实现时，可快速验证兼容性\n\n### Risks\n\n- Mock 过多可能导致与真实服务端行为脱节\n- 测试覆盖度依赖对 spec 的理解完整性\n\n### Effort Estimate\n\n- Size: M（约 2-3 人日）\n- 需要 `pytest`, `requests-mock` / `unittest.mock`\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 仅集成测试 | 验证真实行为 | 依赖外部服务，不稳定 |\n| 仅单元测试 + Mock | 快速、可控 | 可能遗漏真实交互问题 |\n| **单元 + Mock**（推荐） | 平衡速度与覆盖 | 需要维护 mock 逻辑 |\n\n## Test Framework\n\n- `pytest`\n- `requests-mock` 或 `unittest.mock` 用于 HTTP mock\n- `pyproject.toml` 已包含 `requests` 依赖","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"error":"You must read file /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md before overwriting it. Use the Read tool first","time":{"start":1775883472560,"end":1775883472565}}}}
