{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775883502153,"sessionID":"ses_285190f42ffezl6ektvwERVqVL","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae7befd0019AhDIDo24MNXgs","messageID":"msg_d7ae7af9b001gTW6HKo7SgFZUm","sessionID":"ses_285190f42ffezl6ektvwERVqVL","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_d2ee04519e6649dda43dc204","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n2: \n3: ## Summary\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目的 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Purpose\n10: \n11: ### Background\n12: \n13: router、store 和 picod 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件：\n14: - **router**: 负责请求路由、负载均衡和流量管理\n15: - **store**: 负责状态存储、数据持久化和缓存管理\n16: - **picod**: 负责轻量级运行时环境管理和资源调度\n17: \n18: 当前这些模块的测试覆盖不足，需要补充单元测试以确保代码质量。\n19: \n20: ### Goal\n21: \n22: 1. 为 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的单元测试\n23: 2. 提高测试覆盖率到目标水平\n24: 3. 确保关键业务逻辑的测试覆盖\n25: 4. 建立持续测试的基础设施\n26: \n27: ### Value\n28: \n29: - 提高代码质量，减少 regression\n30: - 为重构提供安全网\n31: - 提高开发者信心\n32: - 满足质量门禁要求\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Scope\n37: \n38: ### In-Scope\n39: \n40: - pkg/router 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n41: - pkg/store 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n42: - pkg/picod 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n43: - 关键路径的单元测试\n44: - 边界条件和错误处理测试\n45: - 使用 fake client 或 mock 进行隔离测试\n46: \n47: ### Out-of-Scope\n48: \n49: - 集成测试\n50: - 性能测试\n51: - E2E 测试\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## Acceptance Criteria\n56: \n57: 1. 单元测试通过率 100%\n58: 2. 测试覆盖率目标:\n59:    - router: ≥ 80%\n60:    - store: ≥ 90%\n61:    - picod: ≥ 85%\n62: 3. 所有关键业务逻辑都有对应的测试用例\n63: 4. 测试代码符合 Go 最佳实践\n64: 5. 测试可通过 `go test ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/... ./pkg/picod/...` 执行\n65: 6. 无 flaky tests（确定性结果）\n66: \n67: ---\n68: \n69: ## Detailed Scope Analysis\n70: \n71: ### 1. router 模块\n72: \n73: **文件结构:**\n74: - `server.go` (231 lines) - HTTP 服务器主逻辑\n75: - `backend.go` - 后端池管理\n76: - `proxy.go` - 代理转发\n77: - `route.go` - 路由匹配\n78: - `ratelimit.go` - 限流逻辑\n79: - `auth.go` - 认证\n80: - `jwt.go`, `jwt_handler.go`, `jwt_middleware.go` - JWT 处理\n81: - `session.go`, `session_middleware.go` - 会话管理\n82: - `logging.go` - 日志\n83: - `health.go` - 健康检查\n84: - `config.go` - 配置\n85: \n86: **现有测试:**\n87: - `server_test.go` (167 lines) - 基础初始化测试\n88: \n89: **待测试组件:**\n90: | 组件 | 优先级 | 预估新增行数 |\n91: |------|--------|-------------|\n92: | backend.go | 高 | 150 |\n93: | proxy.go | 高 | 120 |\n94: | route.go | 高 | 100 |\n95: | ratelimit.go | 中 | 80 |\n96: | auth.go | 中 | 60 |\n97: | jwt*.go | 中 | 100 |\n98: | session*.go | 中 | 100 |\n99: | logging.go | 低 | 40 |\n100: | health.go | 低 | 30 |\n101: \n102: **覆盖率目标:** ≥80%\n103: \n104: ### 2. store 模块\n105: \n106: **文件结构:**\n107: - `store.go` (20 lines) - Store 接口定义\n108: - `store_valkey.go` (349 lines) - Valkey 实现\n109: - `store_redis.go` - Redis 实现\n110: - `errors.go` - 错误类型\n111: - `singleton.go` - 单例模式\n112: \n113: **现有测试:** 无\n114: \n115: **测试策略:**\n116: - 使用 mock 或 interface 隔离测试\n117: - 不依赖外部 Valkey/Redis 服务\n118: - 测试所有 Store 接口方法\n119: \n120: **待测试方法:**\n121: | 方法 | 优先级 |\n122: |------|--------|\n123: | Ping | 高 |\n124: | GetSandboxBySessionID | 高 |\n125: | StoreSandbox | 高 |\n126: | UpdateSandbox | 高 |\n127: | DeleteSandboxBySessionID | 高 |\n128: | ListExpiredSandboxes | 中 |\n129: | ListInactiveSandboxes | 中 |\n130: | UpdateSessionLastActivity | 中 |\n131: \n132: **覆盖率目标:** ≥90%\n133: \n134: ### 3. picod 模块\n135: \n136: **文件结构:**\n137: - `server.go` (204 lines) - 主服务器\n138: - `execute.go` - 命令执行\n139: - `files.go` - 文件操作\n140: - `auth.go` - 认证管理\n141: - `config.go` - 配置\n142: - `auth_middleware.go` - 认证中间件\n143: - `health.go` - 健康检查\n144: \n145: **现有测试:**\n146: - `picod_test.go` (833 lines) - 较完整\n147: - `auth_config_test.go`\n148: \n149: **待补充测试:**\n150: - `execute.go` 错误路径\n151: - `files.go` 边界情况\n152: - `auth.go` 边缘情况\n153: - 更多 auth middleware 场景\n154: \n155: **覆盖率目标:** ≥85%\n156: \n157: ---\n158: \n159: ## Impact Analysis\n160: \n161: ### Benefits\n162: \n163: 1. **Increased Reliability**: Comprehensive test coverage reduces regression risk\n164: 2. **Safe Refactoring**: Router, store, and picod operations can be safely modified\n165: 3. **Documentation**: Tests serve as executable documentation\n166: 4. **CI Confidence**: Full test suite enables confident continuous integration\n167: \n168: ### Risks\n169: \n170: 1. **Module Complexity**: Each module has different dependencies and interfaces\n171: 2. **State Management**: Store module testing requires careful state isolation\n172: 3. **External Dependencies**: Some components may require HTTP/gRPC mocking\n173: \n174: ### Estimated Test Files\n175: \n176: - `router/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n177: - `store/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n178: - `picod/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n179: \n180: ---\n181: \n182: ## Implementation Plan\n183: \n184: 1. **Phase 1**: Analyze existing code and identify testing gaps\n185: 2. **Phase 2**: Implement router module tests\n186: 3. **Phase 3**: Implement store module tests  \n187: 4. **Phase 4**: Implement picod module tests\n188: 5. **Phase 5**: Coverage verification and improvements\n189: \n190: ---\n191: \n192: ## Alternatives Considered\n193: \n194: ### 1. 仅集成测试\n195: \n196: **方案:** 不写单元测试，只做集成测试。\n197: \n198: **被拒绝原因:**\n199: - 集成测试需要外部服务（Valkey/Redis）运行\n200: - 测试执行速度慢，不适合 TDD\n201: - 无法精确定位问题所在模块\n202: - CI 环境搭建复杂\n203: \n204: ### 2. 使用第三方测试框架 (ginkgo, testify)\n205: \n206: **方案:** 使用 ginkgo 或 testify 框架。\n207: \n208: **决策:** 继续使用标准 `testing` 包 + `testify/assert`（与现有项目风格一致）\n209: \n210: **被拒绝原因:**\n211: - 现有代码使用标准 `testing` 包\n212: - 避免引入额外依赖\n213: - 保持项目测试风格统一\n214: \n215: ### 3. 使用真实 Valkey/Redis 服务进行测试\n216: \n217: **方案:** 在测试中使用 testcontainer 启动真实数据库服务。\n218: \n219: **被拒绝原因:**\n220: - 测试执行速度慢\n221: - CI 环境配置复杂\n222: - 并发测试困难\n223: - 推荐使用 mock/interface 方案\n224: \n225: ### 4. Property-Based Testing\n226: \n227: **方案:** 使用 `testing/quick` 或 `gopter` 进行属性测试。\n228: \n229: **决策:** 后续迭代考虑，当前聚焦传统单元测试\n230: \n231: **被拒绝原因:**\n232: - 需要更多时间投入\n233: - 传统单元测试优先级更高\n234: - 可在未来迭代中加入\n\n(End of file - total 234 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## Summary\n\n为 AgentCube 项目的 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nrouter、store 和 picod 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件：\n- **router**: 负责请求路由、负载均衡和流量管理\n- **store**: 负责状态存储、数据持久化和缓存管理\n- **picod**: 负责轻量级运行时环境管理和资源调度\n\n当前这些模块的测试覆盖不足，需要补充单元测试以确保代码质量。\n\n### Goal","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775883502135,"end":1775883502150}}}}
